parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt retractor can cause the seatbelt to not retract properly, leading to a loss of protection in the event of an accident, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seatbelt does not retract properly
the seatbelt is fully extended and will not retract
the seatbelt retracts into the door and comes out from the bottom of the door
the seatbelt buckle fails to stay fastened.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of recall parts can prevent the necessary repairs from being made, leaving the vehicle in an unsafe condition and increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The dealer is unable to perform the recall repair due to the unavailability of parts
the owner receives a recall notice but is unable to have the repair done due to the lack of parts.
